rComments: Great professor. I've had him for a few classes. He may be hard to understand at first, but go talk to him during office hoursafter class, and he's very receptive. Nice guy, knows his material. No text books!
Very nice prof, very willing to help you understand concepts/ideas. Very interested in his work...nice to see a prof so engaged with his work. No text book to buy for the course!

Esti de cours plate.. Lectures pas obligatires et évaluations tous à la maison (2 examens maisons et 2 dissertations à faire) Aucun examen en classe mais les travaux comportent la matière enseignée... Esti de prof plate.. WOW.. se répète 3 fois avant de dire quelque chose (ACCOUCHE MON HOMME DIT LE!!)... Wow plate.. Mais facile je dirais.. Plate..

Such a chill prof.  Nice guy too.  Boring (OMG SO BORING) lectures but you learn stuff if you can pay attention.  SUPER easy midterm.  Just study off the slides and the very short readings and you're fine...
Very easy marker. Has a strong French accent, but you learn to understand him after a few classes. Exam is a take home. He knows his stuff.
